        "subject": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Remove RX scale factor",
        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Remove RX scale factor\n\nRX scale factor was used as a tuning variable to control the number\nnumber of posted receives kfilnd may need. But, this information can\nbe derived based on network interface credits and number of immediate\nreceive buffers. Thus, remove RX scale factor.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9347\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Ib40af1ea9606735c900cd8f502c7ae53f648c6bf\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
